<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>sys_ui_related_list_relationship_entry</collection><condition>!current.sys_relationship.nil()</condition><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Abort if has parent entry</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {
	//comment added in Child 4
	// abort if entry for the target related list has this relationship already
	var gr = new GlideRecord('sys_ui_related_list_entry');
	gr.addQuery('related_list', 'REL:' + current.sys_relationship.toString());
	gr.addQuery('list_id', current.sys_ui_related_list.toString());
	gr.query();
	if(gr.getRowCount() > 0) {
		gs.addInfoMessage(gs.getMessage("The '{0}' relationship is already assigned to the '{1}' related list", [current.sys_relationship.name.toString(), current.sys_ui_related_list.calculated_name.toString()]));
		current.setAbortAction(true);
	}

	if(current.sys_relationship.simple_reference.toString() !== 'true')
		return;
	
	// since relationship is a simple reference
	// abort if entry for the target related list has this reference already
	var table = current.sys_relationship.basic_query_from.toString();
	var field = current.sys_relationship.reference_field.toString();
	gr = new GlideRecord('sys_ui_related_list_entry');
	gr.addQuery('related_list', table + '.' + field);
	gr.addQuery('list_id', current.sys_ui_related_list.toString());
	gr.query();
	if(gr.getRowCount() > 0) {
		var td = GlideTableDescriptor.isValid(table) ? GlideTableDescriptor.get(table) : null;
		var tableLabel = td !== null ? td.getED().getLabel() : table;
		var fieldLabel = td !== null && td.isValidField(field) ? td.getElementDescriptor(field).getLabel() : field;
		gs.addInfoMessage(gs.getMessage("The reference field '{0}' on table '{1}' is already assigned to the '{2}' related list", [fieldLabel, tableLabel, current.sys_ui_related_list.calculated_name.toString()]));
		current.setAbortAction(true);
	}
	
})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-06-23 20:39:28</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>7f711fc293300200d9b9941e867ffb2e</sys_id><sys_mod_count>17</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Abort if has parent entry</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Relationship Layout" source="com.glide.ui.relationship_layout">8978aa1775103200832222f29088681a</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_7f711fc293300200d9b9941e867ffb2e</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-01-19 20:52:47</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=7f711fc293300200d9b9941e867ffb2e"/></record_update>
